title: Chicago VII  (7)
description:
Come hell or high water, I will make everyone in the world a Chicago fan.  Somebody explain to me how this band has been overlooked in the Hall of Fame.

The contents of Chicago VII:


Prelude to Aire

Aire

Devil&#039;s Sweet

Italian from New York

Hanky Panky

Life Saver

Happy Man

(I&#039;ve Been) Searchin&#039; So Long

Mongonucleosis

Song of the Evergreens

Byblos

Wishing You Were Here

Call On Me

Women Don&#039;t Want To Love Me

Skinny Boy

Byblos (rehearsal)




The band, the unappreciated musicians:

Bobby Lamm, Pete Cetera, Danny Seraphine, Terry Kath, Lee Loughnane, Walt Parazaider and the one, the only Jimmy Pankow.
